## Physical Details
{% if doc.medium %}**Medium:** {{ doc.medium }}{% endif %}
{% if doc.mediumFormat %}**Format:** {{ doc.mediumFormat }}{% endif %}
{% if doc.condition %}**Condition:** {{ doc.condition }}{% endif %}

{% if doc.state %}**Location:** {{ doc.state }}{% endif %}

{% if doc.subject and doc.subject.size > 0 %}
## Subjects
{{ doc.subject | join: " | " }}
{% endif %}

{% if doc.keywords and doc.keywords.size > 0 %}
## Keywords
{{ doc.keywords | join: " | " }}
{% endif %}

